item.title: US-191 North - Flaming Gorge Dam
item.description: Flaming Gorge Dam on US-191 north. The Flaming Gorge Dam is on the Green River. Behind the dam is Flaming Gorge Reservoir which is part in Utah, and part in Wyoming.
